Jack\u00e9e|date=July 26, 2019|accessdate=July 26, 2019}}</ref>\n\n'''Samples'''\n* {{sup|{{note|a|[a]}}}} \"We Go High\" contains a voice sample of the character [[Navi (The Legend of Zelda)|Navi]], voiced by [[Kaori Mizuhashi]], from ''[[The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time]]'';<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gonintendo.com/stories/340934-new-song-from-chance-the-rapper-features-navi-from-the-legend-of|title=New song from Chance the Rapper features Navi from The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time|website=GoNintendo|date=July 26, 2019|accessdate=July 26, 2019}}</ref> and a vocal sample of a performance by Mike Servin.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B0Y77rgn1pK/|title=JESUS CHRIST love each other forgi ve each other love your enemies JESUS CHRIST @chancetherapper Chance the rapper put the Name Of God JESUS CHRIST on his new album the song is called (we go high) JESUS CHRIST coming out of every platform God bless you Chance the rapper JESUS CHRIST!!!|via=Instagram|author=servinmike20|date=July 25, 2019|accessdate=July 26, 2019}}{{better citation needed|date=July 2019}}</ref>\n* {{sup|{{note|b|[b]}}}} \"Handsome\" contains a sample from \"Honesty\", written by [[Pink Sweats|David Bowden]], and performed by [[Pink Sweats]].<ref name=\"Ken\">{{Cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/chance-the-rapper-releases-new-album-the-big-day-listen/|title=Chance the Rapper Releases New Album ''The Big Day:'' Listen|website=Pitchfork|last=Strauss|first=Matthew|date=July 26, 2019|accessdate=July 26, 2019}}</ref>\n* {{sup|{{note|c|[c]}}}} \"Ballin Flossin\" contains a sample from \"[[I Wanna Be Down]]\", written by [[Keith Crouch|Keith Edward Crouch]], and performed by [[Brandy Norwood|Brandy]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2019/07/26/chance-the-rapper-gets-high-on-michelle-obama-for-big-day/|quote=In \"Ballin Flossin,\" he samples Brandy's 1994 hit \"I Wanna Be Down\" with singer Shawn Mendes.|title=Chance the Rapper gets 'High' on Michelle Obama for 'Big Day'|last=Dellato|first=Marisa|work=NY Post|date=July 26, 2019|accessdate=July 26, 2019}}</ref>\n* {{sup|{{note|d|[d]}}}} \"Get a Bag\" contains a sample from \"Only One\", written and performed by [[James Taylor]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://genius.com/a/chance-the-rapper-samples-james-taylor-s-only-one-on-get-a-bag|title=Chance The Rapper Samples James Taylor On \"Get A Bag\"|website=Genius|last=Welch|first=Isaac|date=July 26, 2019|accessdate=July 26, 2019}}</ref>\n* {{sup|{{note|e|[e]}}}} \"Zanies and Fools\" contains a sample from \"Impossible: It's Possible\" from ''[[Cinderella (musical)|Cinderella]]'', written by [[Oscar Hammerstein II]] and [[Richard Rodgers]], and performed by Rodgers.\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{album chart|Australia|7|artist=Chance the Rapper|album=The Big Day|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 3, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Flanders|45|artist=Chance the Rapper|album=The Big Day|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 2, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Wallonia|181|artist=Chance the Rapper|album=The Big Day|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 2, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|BillboardCanada|3|artist=Chance the Rapper|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 6, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Denmark|16|artist=Chance the Rapper|album=The Big Day|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 7, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Netherlands|16|artist=Chance the Rapper|album=The Big Day|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 2, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|France|160|artist=Chance the Rapper|album=The Big Day|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 12, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Ireland2|18|artist=Chance the Rapper|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 3, 2019}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Lithuanian Albums ([[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.agata.lt/lt/naujienos/savaites-klausomiausi-w16-2-2-2-2-2-3-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2/|title=Savait\u0117s klausomiausi (TOP 100)|lang