er.com/read?oid=076&aid=0003039121|title='\uc2ac\ub7a8\ub369\ud06c2' \uae40\uc219\u00b7\ud64d\uc9c4\uacbd\u00b7\uac15\uc608\uc6d0\u00b7\ud55c\ucc44\uc601\u00b7\ud64d\uc9c4\uc601\u00b7\uacf5\ubbfc\uc9c0\u00b7\uc804\uc18c\ubbf8 7\u4eba\ud655\uc815(\uacf5\uc2dd)|website=Naver|date=January 16, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Idol Drama Operation Team]]''\n| \uc544\uc774\ub3cc \ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 \uacf5\uc791\ub2e8\n| align=\"center\"| [[Korean Broadcasting System|KBS Joy]]\n| <ref name=IDOT>{{cite web|last1=Hwang|first1=Soo-yeon|title=KBS \uce21 \"'\uc544\uc774\ub3cc \ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 \uacf5\uc791\ub2e8' \uc2ac\uae30X\uc18c\ubbf8 \ucd9c\uc5f0 \ud655\uc815\"(\uacf5\uc2dd)|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=112&aid=0002906127|website=Naver|publisher=Herald Pop|accessdate=March 28, 2017|language=ko}}</ref>{{efn|''Idol Drama Operation Team'' premiered on May 29, 2017 via Naver TV Cast and Naver V Live. It was then broadcast on KBS Joy and KBS World channel every Mondays, Wednesdays and Fridays, starting June 10.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hwang|first1=Soo-yeon|title=[M+\ucd08\uc810] '\uc544\uc774\ub3cc \ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 \uacf5\uc791\ub2e8' \ubcf8\ubc29 \uc804\ubd80\ud130 \ud1b5\ud55c '\uac78\uadf8\ub8f9\uc758 \uc9c4\uc2ec'|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=057&aid=0001115419|website=Naver|publisher=MBN|accessdate=May 1, 2017|language=ko}}</ref><ref name=\"IDOT KBS\"/>}}\n|-\n| ''[[I Can See Your Voice (South Korean TV series)|I Can See Your Voice]]''\n| \ub108\uc758 \ubaa9\uc18c\ub9ac\uac00 \ubcf4\uc5ec\n| [[Mnet (TV channel)|Mnet]]\n| Detective (Season 4 Episode 4 - 5)\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2019\n| ''[[Not the Same Person You Used to Know]]''\n| \ub2c8\uac00 \uc54c\ub358 \ub0b4\uac00 \uc544\ub0d0\n| [[Mnet (TV channel)|Mnet]]\n| Protagonist (Season 2 Episode 1)\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sports.chosun.com/news/ntype.htm?id=201906290100214010014618&servicedate=20190628|title='\ub2c8\uac00 \uc54c\ub358 \ub0b4\uac00 \uc544\ub0d0 V2' \uc804\uc18c\ubbf8, \ub3d9\uc0dd \uc5d0